0","default":"<p>Restore mitochondrial function to efficiently convert food into energy</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLbP0pen7l_childItem_1","label":"ggLbP0pen7l_childItem_1","default":"<p>Reduce oxidative stress and repair damaged cells</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLbP0pen7l_childItem_2","label":"ggLbP0pen7l_childItem_2","default":"<p>Support better sleep, balanced mood, and improved vitality</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4g_hSQJm6_text","label":"gg4g_hSQJm6_text","default":"<p>Feel revitalized from the inside out. With Rosabella Moringa, you’re harnessing the power of nature’s most nutrient-dense plant to reclaim your energy, balance, and resilience.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYM7_wi2uE_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYM7_wi2uE_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1734001732-ims_shape.svg"}],
